Build instructions for the Apache Lucy C library
================================================

When building under UNIX and derivatives run:

    $ ./configure
    $ make
    $ make test

When building under Windows with MSVC run:

    $ configure.bat
    $ nmake
    $ nmake test

Configuration
-------------

    ./configure [ options ] [ -- cflags ]

Options include

    --enable-coverage
        Enable code coverage. Create HTML pages with coverage data using
        lcov by running "make coverage".

